SourceString: This Build Gun software upgrade adds a new tab to the Build Menu: The Customizer. From here pioneers have access to the Color section, as well as Material and Pattern options, which can be purchased in the AWESOME Shop.
Awesome new products will become available in the AWESOME Shop upon obtaining this Milestone.
This Build Gun software upgrade adds the Blueprint tab to the Build Menu. From the Blueprint tab, pioneers are able to access and organize the Blueprints created with the Blueprint Designer.
A by-product of Plastic and Rubber production. Can be further refined into Fuel and Petroleum Coke.
A by-product of Crude Oil refinement into Fuel. Commonly used to manufacture Plastic and Rubber.
Awesome new products will become available in the AWESOME Shop upon obtaining this Milestone.
